Usage: deletePowerSwitch [-help] [-1801PowerSwitchRuleName <string>]
                         [-instanceList <string>] [-isCustomChain]
                         [-powerDomain <string>] [-column | -ring]

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
-1801PowerSwitchRuleName <string>     # (string, optional)
-column                               # (bool, optional)
-instanceList <string>                # (string, optional)
-isCustomChain                        # (bool, optional)
-powerDomain <string>                 # (string, optional)
-ring                                 # (bool, optional)